{"tid":1070642,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Juno謝安琪《寂寞就如》《其實寂寞》","createTime":"2019-03-20T20:42:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-21T11:19:29.000Z","uid":160973,"like":11,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"bdeb16861c2b97da5be23e58d83eb8fa12544467","tid":1070642,"uid":160973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T20:42:54.000Z","msg":"Juno與謝安琪，繼續以董折和浦銘心的故事拉扯我們潛藏內心的那道傷痕，二人同步推出《其實寂寞》與《寂寞就如》兩首新歌，轉眼間已登上各大平台的第一位。日前（3月17日）Juno終於發布大家期侍已久嘅mv，呢個MV出咗兩日點擊率更突破四萬大關，對於Juno破格地將兩首歌嘅MV合二為一，網民都大讚做得好，仲話好歌一定要連住聽。<br />\n<br />\n一對情侶分手過後，感受最深的，大概是那股突如其來的寂寞：空空洞洞，又無法擺脫。無論你習慣不習慣，也要接受自己已是一個人。《其實寂寞》與《寂寞就如》，淡淡道出二人如何跟眼前這份寂寞互動，同樣寂寞，來到男和女身上，原來可以發酵成兩樣心情。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2Fh2k09\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Fh2k09&d=01EY%2BZdPKRb21p6QCrTOV9OJZs7QJHlESVJdSYWWwTM%3D&h=3f4a156f\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2Fh2k09</a>"},{"pid":"10d6c26b199051a4f711bf7471ca9f7a698245c8","tid":1070642,"uid":40470,"like":5,"dislike":6,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T23:24:12.000Z","msg":"Kay果首頭幾句歌詞敗筆<br />\n<br />\n數白檻咁，即刻唔想聽<br />\n<br />\n但中段其好"},{"pid":"f25b617030012100cf123bb2ee3ed4dee4eb9c45","tid":1070642,"uid":214581,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T00:18:22.000Z","msg":"埋頭狂吃通粉不會淋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cabc6a8faa479261c6f87802c5bf834007df1e5f","tid":1070642,"uid":162361,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T00:41:51.000Z","msg":"仲以為係陳詠謙大師填詞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2504b1d8a99d941437ebdbbd582463ebc74201d3","tid":1070642,"uid":4401,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T02:29:33.000Z","msg":"寂寞就自己一個打飛機<br />\n即使想戒J, 家裡沒有避<br />\n無謂謂未傷身，數數飛機打幾多次<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8537458ebf602e86f84e8028459bc2410655f082","tid":1070642,"uid":149833,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T11:19:29.000Z","msg":"一聽就覺得真係林夕嘅詞？<br />\n到「好驚俾蟻咬 無人類過問」<br />\n感覺好陳詠謙<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n「其實寂寞\t就如自己一個看山火」<br />\n看花火會唔會適合啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}